    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has clearly been well-maintained. The engine runs smoothly, and all major mechanical systems are in solid working order, making it a reliable choice for your next car. The exterior paint still holds a great luster, though you will find some minor signs of use, such as a few small stone chips on the hood and a light scuff on the rear passenger door. Inside, the upholstery is clean and free of tears, though there is some light wear on the driver's seat bolster. All electronics, including the infotainment system and climate control, function as intended. It is a great example of a used vehicle that has been cared for properly and is ready for many more miles.",
